dump            traj all custom ${DUMPEVERY} trajectories/${MODEL}_ramp_${STAGE}.lammpstrj id type xu yu zu
dump            traj all custom 100 trajectories/${MODEL}_ramp_${STAGE}.lammpstrj id type xu yu zu
